        <h1>Dead Hang World Record: 80 Minutes 41 Seconds</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">The dead hang world record is 80 minutes 41 seconds, set by Kenta Adachi of Japan on 18 November 2022 and verified by Guinness World Records. This page documents the record holders, how the record has progressed over time, and the training behind it. Want to take on a challenge yourself or compete with friends? See our <a href="/community/">dead hang community</a> page for group challenges and leaderboards.</p>
      </header>
