            <tr><td>Previous holder of the same title</td><td>Annie Judis</td><td>USA</td><td>Set at age 81</td><td>2024</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>Outside the record books, lower average bodyweight gives women a favorable strength to weight ratio for hanging, and trained female climbers and grip athletes commonly hold dead hangs beyond 3 minutes.</p>

        <h2 id="record-history">Dead Hang Record History &amp; Timeline</h2>
        <p>The dead hang has evolved from an obscure grip training exercise to a competitive discipline with an official Guinness world record, organized competitions and a growing community of athletes.</p>

